snippet.title: Paramedics rush to crash on major Coast road
snippet.content:
BREAKING: Paramedics are rushing to the scene of a crash on a major Sunshine Coast road.
The crash was reported to emergency services at 2.25pm from Caloundra Rd, near the Bruce Hwy.
Initial reports suggest a vehicle has crashed into a barrier on the left-hand shoulder of the westbound lanes.
One ambulance crew has just arrived at the scene.
More to come.
